<p>When I started as a lecturer I fell in love with speaking and teaching students new skills. After a year or so I asked myself; 'Why keep this all this stuff I and students are learning inside the classroom?'. After that I started sharing my knowledge at meet-ups but that quickly turned into giving guest-lectures at companies. Things escalated  and I was regularly asked to talk at conferences, schools and other companies with growing audiences. </p>

