<h2>Talks</h2>

<p>I'd like to talk about tech, building for the web and tinkering with code. Some of my talks are technical with code examples. I'm fascinated by how people interact and spend their time in this digital age.</p>

<p>My brief talks are around ~30 minutes and are well suited for office talks and meet-ups at your company. These talks are full of practical tips, short examples and lots of resources for you to get back to work.</p>

